           <string>对每个所选顶点，查找与其不相连的最近顶点，并从所选顶点向该最近顶点创建一条边。在可能时，面会被自动创建。</string>
          </property>
          <property name="text">
           <string>与最近处桥接</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
       </layout>
      </item>
      <item>
       <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="horizontalLayout_9">
        <property name="spacing">
         <number>1</number>
        </property>
        <property name="topMargin">
         <number>0</number>
        </property>
        <item>
         <widget class="QPushButton" name="modify_snap">
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>对每个所选顶点，查找参考网格上最近的顶点，并将所选顶点移动到该参考顶点的位置。</string>
          </property>
          <property name="text">
           <string>吸附到参考顶点</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item>
         <widget class="QPushButton" name="modify_straighten">
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>查找当前顶点选择的端点，并尝试将它们对齐为一条直线，随后每个对齐的顶点贴合到参考网格。</string>
          </property>
          <property name="text">
           <string>拉直</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
       </layout>
      </item>
      <item>
       <spacer name="verticalSpacer_5">
        <property name="orientation">
         <enum>Qt::Vertical</enum>
        </property>
        <property name="sizeHint" stdset="0">
         <size>
          <width>20</width>
          <height>20</height>
         </size>
        </property>
       </spacer>
      </item>
      <item>
       <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="horizontalLayout_21">
        <property name="spacing">
         <number>2</number>
        </property>
        <property name="topMargin">
         <number>0</number>
        </property>
        <item>
         <layout class="QFormLayout" name="formLayout_6">
          <property name="topMargin">
           <number>0</number>
          </property>
          <item row="0" column="0">
           <widget class="QLabel" name="label_6">
            <property name="text">
             <string>距参考距离</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item row="0" column="1">
           <widget class="QDoubleSpinBox" name="modify_inflateDistance">
            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>设置“膨胀”操作使顶点远离其当前位置的距离。</string>
            </property>
            <property name="decimals">
             <number>3</number>
            </property>
            <property name="minimum">
             <double>-9999999.990000000223517</double>
            </property>
            <property name="maximum">
             <double>9999999.990000000223517</double>
            </property>
            <property name="value">
             <double>1.000000000000000</double>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </item>
       </layout>
      </item>
      <item>
       <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="horizontalLayout_16">
        <property name="spacing">
         <number>1</number>
        </property>
        <property name="topMargin">
         <number>0</number>
        </property>
        <item>
         <widget class="QPushButton" name="modify_inflate">
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>沿每个顶点的法线方向，按给定距离（检查器视图“修改”面板中的“距参考距离”参数）使其远离参考网格表面。</string>
          </property>
          <property name="text">
           <string>膨胀</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item>
         <widget class="QPushButton" name="modify_conform">
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>将每个所选顶点贴合到参考网格。它会为每个顶点找到参考网格表面的最近点，并将顶点移动到该位置。参考网格表面的最近点不一定是参考网格的顶点位置。</string>
          </property>
          <property name="text">
           <string>贴合</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
       </layout>
      </item>
     </layout>
    </widget>
   </item>
   <item>
    <widget class="QGroupBox" name="groupBox_5">
     <property name="title">
